# Package Map — Viseed CMS Monorepo

> **Khi thêm/xoá package, plugin, hoặc app → cập nhật file này ngay.**

## Packages (`packages/`)

| Package | Npm scope | Mô tả | Được import bởi |
|---|---|---|---|
| `packages/viseed` | `@viseed/cms` | **Umbrella package** — re-export từ tất cả `@viseed/*` core, include admin dist, expose CLI bin `viseed` | end-users |
| `packages/types` | `@viseed/types` | TypeScript interfaces/types ONLY — không có runtime logic | Tất cả packages, plugins, apps |
| `packages/validator` | `@viseed/validator` | Zod schemas cho content, user, media, plugin | `@viseed/core`, plugins, admin |
| `packages/schema` | `@viseed/schema` | Drizzle base tables (`users`, `sessions`, `installed_plugins`, `media_files`, **`widgets`**), `mergeSchemas()` helper | `@viseed/core`, plugins |
| `packages/core` | `@viseed/core` | `ViseedCMS` class, `HookRegistry`, `createDatabase()`, `LocalStorageAdapter`, core media routes (`/api/media`), static admin serve, **`WidgetTypeRegistry`**, widget CRUD API, public widget hydration routes | plugins, apps, CLI |
| `packages/registry` | `@viseed/registry` | `PluginRegistryClient` — fetch plugin list, install/uninstall, verify SHA-256 integrity | `@viseed/core`, `@viseed/ui` |
| `packages/ui` | `@viseed/ui` | Vue `ComponentRegistry`, `themeWidgetRegistry` (theme extension widgets by slot), base components, Plugin Marketplace UI | `apps/admin`, plugins |
| `packages/cli` | `@viseed/cli` | CLI commands: `viseed init`, `viseed db push/generate/migrate`, `viseed plugin install/uninstall`. **Published** — là runtime dependency của `@viseed/cms` (umbrella re-export bin `viseed`); end-user cài `@viseed/cms` sẽ kéo theo cli | `@viseed/cms`, standalone binary |
| `packages/config` | `@viseed/config` | Shared tsconfig (`tsconfig.base.json`, `tsconfig.app.json`, `tsconfig.lib.json`). **Private** | Tất cả packages |

## Plugins (`plugins/`)

> Plugins là **Official plugins** — npm packages, cần `bun add` + restart.
> Khác với Community plugins (CDN bundle, dynamic import không cần restart).

| Plugin | Npm package | Tính năng |
|---|---|---|
| `plugins/plugin-auth` | `@viseed/plugin-auth` | Schema + routes cho authentication (đăng ký, đăng nhập, sessions) |
| `plugins/plugin-blog` | `@viseed/plugin-blog` | Posts/categories schema + CRUD REST routes + admin views (PostsView, CategoriesView) |
| `plugins/plugin-common-widgets` | `@viseed/plugin-common-widgets` | Common widget types: `common-widgets/tabs` (vertical/horizontal tabs với rich content), `common-widgets/qa` (single-open accordion Q&A). No schema, no routes — chỉ widget types với admin config forms + public renderers |
| `plugins/plugin-menu` | `@viseed/plugin-menu` | Menu management — schema + CRUD REST routes + admin view (MenusView). Injects `menuMain`/`menuFooter` into theme context via `theme:beforeRender` hook |
| `plugins/plugin-pages` | `@viseed/plugin-pages` | Standalone pages schema + CRUD routes, `theme:beforeRender` data injection + admin view (PagesView) |

## Themes (`themes/`)

> Themes là **built-in default themes** — đã đăng ký sẵn trong registry, user dùng ngay không cần cài thêm.
> Một thời điểm chỉ có 1 theme active, nhưng registry giữ nhiều themes để hot-swap.

| Theme | Npm package | Mô tả |
|---|---|---|
| `themes/theme-blog` | `@viseed/theme-blog` | Blog theme — Eta templates, settings schema, static assets. Factory `blogTheme()` |
| `themes/theme-insurance` | `@viseed/theme-insurance` | Insurance product theme — Eta templates (home/category/post/404), companion plugin for home carousel, full settings schema. Factory `insuranceTheme()` |

## Apps (`apps/`)

| App | Filter name | Mô tả | Port mặc định |
|---|---|---|---|
| `apps/admin` | `@viseed/admin` | Vue 3 SPA admin dashboard, build output embed vào `core/dist/admin`. Built-in views: Dashboard, Content, Media, **Widgets** (order 25), Plugins, Themes… | 5173 (dev) |
| `apps/docs` | `@viseed/docs` | VitePress documentation site | 5174 |
